		</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="0ACF587E0D3F32C6FB88">
			<name>Massive Refinery + Petrochemical</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<p><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">ExxonMobil</span></span> Baytown complex near <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Baytown</span></span>, and it is one of the largest integrated refining and petrochemical facilities in the world.<br></p><p>What you are seeing is not just a single refinery, but a huge integrated industrial system that includes:<br></p><ul><li>crude oil refinery<br></li><li>petrochemical plants<br></li><li>olefins units<br></li><li>aromatics units<br></li><li>storage tank farms<br></li><li>utility systems<br></li><li>pipeline terminals<br></li><li>docks and marine loading facilities.<br></li></ul><h1>What Happens There<br></h1><p>A refinery like this takes crude oil and separates/converts it into products such as:<br></p><div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead><tr><th>Product<br></th><th>Use<br></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Gasoline<br></td><td>cars<br></td></tr><tr><td>Diesel<br></td><td>trucks/shipping<br></td></tr><tr><td>Jet fuel<br></td><td>aviation<br></td></tr><tr><td>LPG<br></td><td>heating/petrochemicals<br></td></tr><tr><td>Naphtha<br></td><td>petrochemical feedstock<br></td></tr><tr><td>Fuel oil<br></td><td>marine/power<br></td></tr><tr><td>Petrochemical feedstocks<br></td><td>plastics/chemicals<br></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
