			<name>Zhenhai Refining &amp; Chemical</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5"><b>Owner / Operator:</b> Sinopec<br><b>Crude capacity:</b> ~345,000–540,000 bpd (expanding toward ~800,000)<br><b>Specialisation:</b> One of China's largest integrated refining and petrochemical sites (Ningbo). Figures vary by source and expansion phase.</div>]]></description>
