			<name>Dalian Petrochemical</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5"><b>Owner / Operator:</b> PetroChina (CNPC)<br><b>Crude capacity:</b> ~400,000–410,000 bpd (~20.5 Mt/y)<br><b>Specialisation:</b> Major refinery in north-east China (Liaoning). Some units reportedly facing restructuring.</div>]]></description>
