		<Placemark id="004987E8B03FA09C66A7">
			<name>The Shell Rheinland refinery complex</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<h1>Shell Energy and Chemicals Park Rheinland<br></h1><p>or<br></p><h1>Rheinland Raffinerie Shell<br></h1><p>The full industrial complex is located south of <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Cologne</span></span> along the <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Rhine River</span></span> between:<br></p><ul><li>Godorf<br></li><li>Wesseling<br></li></ul><p>The complex consists of two major sites:<br></p><ul><li>Werk Nord (Godorf)<br></li><li>Werk Süd (Wesseling)<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>BEST Google Earth coordinates<br></h1><h2>Main Godorf refinery area<br></h2><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>50.855, 6.980</span></code><br></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><h2>Wesseling refinery/chemical area<br></h2><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>50.817, 7.007</span></code><br></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><h2>Entire Rheinland complex center<br></h2><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>50.836, 6.993</span></code><br></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><div><hr><br></div><h1>Professional location description<br></h1><p>You can save it in Google Earth as:<br></p><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Shell Rheinland Refinery Complex</span><br><span>(Godorf + Wesseling)</span><br><span>Cologne / Rhine Corridor</span><br><span>Germany</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><p>Or shorter:<br></p><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Shell Rheinland Refinery</span></code><br></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><div><hr><br></div><h1>What makes this site important<br></h1><p>This is:<br></p><ul><li>Germany’s largest refinery complex<br></li><li>directly connected to Rotterdam by pipeline<br></li><li>integrated into Rhine barge logistics<br></li><li>linked to CEPS/NATO fuel infrastructure<br></li><li>one of Europe’s key refining hubs<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>What you should visually identify on satellite imagery<br></h1><h2>Godorf (north section)<br></h2><p>Look for:<br></p><ul><li>dense refining units<br></li><li>hydrocrackers<br></li><li>flare stacks<br></li><li>pipeline manifolds<br></li></ul><h2>Wesseling (south section)<br></h2><p>Look for:<br></p><ul><li>petrochemical units<br></li><li>storage areas<br></li><li>utilities<br></li><li>Rhine terminals<br></li></ul><h2>Along the Rhine<br></h2><p>Look for:<br></p><ul><li>barge docks<br></li><li>loading jetties<br></li><li>crude/product transfer infrastructure<br></li></ul><div><br></div><h1>VERY important infrastructure insight<br></h1><p>This complex is fed by:<br></p><ul><li>Rotterdam crude imports<br></li><li>the Rotterdam–Rhine Pipeline<br></li><li>Rhine barges<br></li></ul><p>And distributes products through:<br></p><ul><li>pipelines<br></li><li>barges<br></li><li>rail<br></li><li>trucks<br></li></ul><p>This is one of the core nodes of the:<br></p><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>ARA → Rhine → Ruhr</span></code><br></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><p>energy corridor.<br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
			<LookAt>
