			<name>Bayernoil Refinery Vohburg</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5"><b>Owner / Operator:</b> Bayernoil JV (Varo Energy ~51%, Rosneft ~29%, Eni 20%)<br><b>Crude capacity:</b> Part of the Bayernoil complex (~206,000 bpd across both sites)<br><b>Specialisation:</b> Second Bayernoil site, operated jointly with Neustadt as a single operation. Fed by the Trans-Alpine Pipeline (TAL); supplies Bavaria and northern Austria.</div>]]></description>
