			<name>RAPID Storage &amp; terminals</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>The storage/loading facility<br></div><li><div>Includes :&nbsp;<span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Vopak</span></span> Pengerang storage terminal + Other independent storage (like Dialog facilities nearby)<br></div></li><li><div>Used for : Storing, Blending, Export/import<br></div></li><div><br></div>]]></description>
