		<Placemark id="02411B8AE03EB8C242B1">
			<name>ATPC Antwerp Terminal and Processing Company</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<h1>⚙️ What it is<br></h1><p>ATPC is a <b>tank storage and processing terminal</b>, not a refinery.<br></p><h3>It handles:<br></h3><ul><li>🛢️ Oil products (diesel, gasoline components)<br></li><li>🧪 Chemicals (petrochemical feedstocks, intermediates)<br></li><li>🔄 Blending and handling of liquids<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>🧭 What you’re seeing in your image<br></h1><p>You can clearly identify:<br></p><h3>🟢 Storage tanks<br></h3><ul><li>The many <b>white circular tanks</b><br></li><li>Used to store liquids safely<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h3>🟡 Processing / blending area<br></h3><ul><li>Central zone with pipes and equipment<br></li><li><div>Used to:<br></div><ul><li>mix products<br></li><li>adjust specifications<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h3>🔵 Jetty (top of image)<br></h3><ul><li>Ships dock there<br></li><li>Load/unload liquids<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h3>⚫ Rail / truck loading (bottom)<br></h3><ul><li>Long rectangular structures<br></li><li>Used to distribute products inland<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>🔗 How ATPC fits in Antwerp<br></h1><p>ATPC sits inside the larger:<br></p><h2><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Port of Antwerp petrochemical cluster</span></span><br></h2><p>👉 It connects:<br></p><ul><li>Refineries (ExxonMobil, TotalEnergies)<br></li><li>Petrochemical plants (BASF, INEOS)<br></li><li>Global shipping routes<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>🧠 What role it plays<br></h1><p>Think of ATPC as:<br></p><pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><br></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Storage + mixing + distribution hub</span><br></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><br></div></div></div></div></div></pre><p>👉 It:<br></p><ul><li>Stores products temporarily<br></li><li>Blends them to required specs<br></li><li><div>Sends them onward by:<br></div><ul><li>ship<br></li><li>pipeline<br></li><li>rail<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
