			<name>Port Louis</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Mauritius is a <b>bunkering and redistribution point</b><br></p><ul><li><div>Ships passing through the <b>Indian Ocean trade routes</b> can:<br></div><ul><li>Refuel (LSFO, marine fuel)<br></li><li>Offload cargo<br></li></ul></li><li><div>If Singapore is not profitable:<br></div><ul><li>Traders send fuel here instead<br></li></ul></li></ul><p>➡️ It acts as a <b>secondary hub replacing Singapore flows</b><br></p><div><br></div><div>Main port of MauritiusHandles <b>almost all imports</b>, including petroleum productsActs as a <b>regional transshipment hub</b> (ships refuel and redistribute cargo)<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
